    {
        "content": "<p>I don't quite get that one. Should that not be \"When you know JavaScript... \" ? Everything is an object kind of idea, and no typing? (I hesitate to say but it could also be \"When you know Lisp...\")</p>",
        "id": 221421025,
        "sender_full_name": "Henry Story",
        "timestamp": 1609626922
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I think the joke is that when you know categories, you try to force everything into the language of category theory</p>",
        "id": 221423566,
        "sender_full_name": "John van de Wetering",
        "timestamp": 1609630760
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>\"when all you have is a hammer\", that kind of idea</p>",
        "id": 221423572,
        "sender_full_name": "John van de Wetering",
        "timestamp": 1609630778
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>\"When all you have is a hammer\" implies one is using the wrong tool for the job, but in the video, the demonstrated solution was the most elegant.</p>",
        "id": 221424097,
        "sender_full_name": "Nathanael Arkor",
        "timestamp": 1609631753
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Spoken like a true category theorist :)</p>",
        "id": 221424210,
        "sender_full_name": "John van de Wetering",
        "timestamp": 1609631972
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I think the comparison is amusing and apt: the power of category theory lies in its abstraction, and if a single technique suffices to solve several problems, there is no need to waste time coming up with a unique solution for each one.</p>",
        "id": 221424213,
        "sender_full_name": "Nathanael Arkor",
        "timestamp": 1609631982
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/steveklabnik/status/1349044902919868419?s=19\">https://twitter.com/steveklabnik/status/1349044902919868419?s=19</a> this is a good one.</p>\n<div class=\"inline-preview-twitter\"><div class=\"twitter-tweet\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/steveklabnik/status/1349044902919868419?s=19\"><img class=\"twitter-avatar\" src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1302650353557680130/6m9uvvjF_normal.jpg\"></a><p><a href=\"https://t.co/K9fGSfB6g1\">https://twitter.com/steveklabnik/status/1349044902919868419/photo/1</a></p><span>- steveklabnik (@steveklabnik)</span><div class=\"twitter-image\"><a href=\"https://t.co/K9fGSfB6g1\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ErjFLmlWMAAjCee.jpg:thumb\"></a></div></div></div>",
        "id": 222533098,
